subject: Automobile Racing
Automobiles
Nascar Nextel Cup Series
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: The racecars that Jimmie Johnson and others put in victory lane over the years are for sale and a bargain these days, now that Nascar has made most of the racecars used in the Nextel Cup series obsolete.
